Group of Executives to Buy Luminar Clubs, Financial Times Say

-- B y   A m b e r e e n   C h o u d h u r y
-- 
2011-12-10T08:32:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-10/group-of-executives-to-buy-luminar-clubs-financial-times-say.html
The administrators of  Luminar Group
Holdings Plc (LMR)  agreed to sell about 60 clubs to a group of leisure
industry executives for 45 million pounds ($70.5 million)
excluding debt, the Financial Times newspaper said.  The group includes former Luminar Executive Director Peter
Marks, Joe Heanen and Alex Geffert, according to the report,
citing a statement.  To contact the reporters on this story:
